 to make someone bald ? You got it!\nWant to create a colourful punk hairstyle ? You got it!\nWant to regrow hair from scratch ? That's right - You got it!\n\nA variety of tools available:\n* a list of trimmers for a fun trimming look\n* a razorblade for that nice close shave\n* a lot of differently colored spray cans for a colourful experience\n* a hair grower, because we believe in science\n* a water spray bottle for some wetness\n* a hairdryer for some dryness\n* a comb for visual reasons\n* a cactus for undisclosed reasons\n* and more", "short_description": "A casual barbershop game where the player's objective is to serve a client by matching client's needs using many tools at the player's disposal or just have raw creative fun. \n\nWant to make someone bald ? You got it!\nWant to create a colourful punk hairstyle ? You got it!\nWant to regrow hair from scratch ? That's right - You got it!"}]}, "developer_name": "HyperVR Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hypervr.games/privacy/shavenstuff.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "HyperVR Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://shavenstuff.hypervr.games/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "574140241012150"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 35, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1028406852077064"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", 